name: Amunets Server Transfer - v1.0.17
description:
[b]Mod-ID[/b]: 2305969565

A server cluster solution for conan.
This mod allows switching "on the fly" between servers (and taking your character with you).
changeNote:
2021-01-04 - 1.0.17
- force saving of a character after import.
- retry once if item failed to spawn in.
- log an error to the server log if item spawn failed twice.
- cluster.php now keeps a backup of the last import to make admin life easier.
author: LilMissHentai
